      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Here are the results for your query about Popper's *The Logic of Scientific Discovery* and its publication by Hutchinson in 1959:\n\n"
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "*The Logic of Scientific Discovery* is a 1959 book about the philosophy of science by the philosopher Karl Popper."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Popper rewrote his book in English from the 1934 (imprint '1935') German original, titled *Logik der Forschung*."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\nRegarding the publisher: "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "The first English edition was published in 1959 by Hutchinson & Co."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": " The full bibliographic reference is typically cited as: "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Popper, Karl R., *The logic of scientific discovery*, Hutchinson & Co., Ltd., London, 1959, 480 pp."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\n"
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "First published in English in 1959, this book revolutionized contemporary thinking about science and knowledge. It was also originally published in New York by Basic Books in 1959."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\nThe book was later reissued by other publishers: "
      },
      {
        "citations": [],
        "type": "text",
        "text": "It was first published by Routledge in 1992, and then in Routledge Classics in 2002."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "\n\nSo to summarize, **Hutchinson & Co.** (London) was the British publisher of the first English edition in 1959, while Basic Books was the American publisher."
      }
